### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8004
@pizzaStoreUrl = http://localhost:8001
@pizzaKitchenUrl = http://localhost:8002
@pizzaDeliveryUrl = http://localhost:8003

### Start a new pizza order workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/start-order
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "order_id": "1",
    "pizza_type": "pepperoni",
    "size": "large",
    "customer": {
        "name": "John Doe",
        "address": "123 Main St",
        "phone": "555-0123"
    }
}

### Validate pizza (approve)
POST {{baseUrl}}/validate-pizza
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "order_id": "1",
    "approved": true
}

### Validate pizza (reject)
POST {{baseUrl}}/validate-pizza
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "order_id": "123",
    "approved": false
}

